metadata.name: Golden Gamer Plaque - nasjaq
metadata.description:
A golden plaque embossed with a relief of the mannys.game logo, celebrating a gamer who's reached 1000 or more points on https://mannys.game/leaderboard - The plaque is adorned with the gamer's name on the front and their statistics on the back.

Plaque #1 was won by nasjaq on 09-16-2021.
